title: [SOLVED]820-2610 Fails Internal Vid. Test 72; Dying MCP/GPU or MUX?
message:
Working on an 820-2610 that had no power; replaced the problem cap as per usual and got life. Unit seems to be working well, but fails ASD test #72 for internal video, specifically the "Fill Rect 2D Acceleration..." test.

Is this an issue related to the MCP/GPU or the MUX? Is there anything I can do to see if there really is an issue (furmark, etc), or should I run EFI to see if it fails there as well? 

All help appreciated--thanks!
